# Interpreting recalc.py Output

Example:
```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "total_errors": 0,
  "total_formulas": 42
}
```

If errors exist:
```json
{
  "status": "errors_found",
  "error_summary": {
    "#REF!": {
      "count": 2,
      "locations": ["Sheet1!B5"]
    }
  }
}
```

