	('e29b865f-8887-4865-9704-eab30f28e53c', 'c15f870d-1d60-4442-b823-cabd7ca520e4', 'sevt_01YDDfTwt8y5aHGsbwdtXBgC', 'agent.message', '{"id": "sevt_01YDDfTwt8y5aHGsbwdtXBgC", "type": "agent.message", "content": [{"text": "Boom! 🧃 I''ve squeezed out a fresh PowerPoint presentation all about juices! \n\nHere''s what I''ve extracted from the juice press for you:\n\n**8 slides of pure juice goodness:**\n1. **Title Slide** - Bold intro to get things started\n2. **What is Juice?** - The fundamentals of this liquid gold\n3. **The Juice Universe** - Different juice types from apple to green\n4. **Health Benefits** - Why juice is actually amazing for you\n5. **Juice Trends** - Cold-pressed, organic, cleanses, shots, and more\n6. **Pro Tips** - How to keep your juice fresh and potent\n7. **Juice Philosophy** - The deeper meaning of drinking juice\n8. **Closing Slide** - A motivational send-off\n\nThe presentation is all colorful, has fun emojis, and covers everything from basic juice facts to trends. You''ve got all the juicy details you could ask for! 🍊🥤\n\nYour file is ready to download: **JUICE_PRESENTATION.pptx**", "type": "text"}], "processed_at": "2026-05-09T23:26:58.989Z"}', '2026-05-09 23:26:58.989+00', '2026-05-09 23:27:00.958089+00'),
