	('1129b4d8-d7f8-4d9b-ba1a-8cd2f4c10956', 'ae6275c4-6918-4909-ab6a-8fc318669419', 'sevt_01Q7fuuYXpaUNhXbhpYUUjkY', 'agent.message', '{"id": "sevt_01Q7fuuYXpaUNhXbhpYUUjkY", "type": "agent.message", "content": [{"text": "Got it! The file is too large to attach directly, but I can help you. To transform your FY26 presentation into a gerbil-themed masterpiece while keeping the theme intact, I have a couple of options:\n\n1. **You can download and re-upload** a smaller version or specific slides\n2. **You can sync the file** using this link first: `/kb/files/0fec38c6-f043-423f-8b47-531584bda56c/sync-to-anthropic`\n\nWhich would work better for you? Or do you have the presentation available locally that you could upload to the session? 🧃 Once I can access it, I''ll extract the content, keep all the original design theming and structure, and gerbil-ify the text and visuals! 🐹", "type": "text"}], "processed_at": "2026-05-10T03:17:52.915Z"}', '2026-05-10 03:17:52.915+00', '2026-05-10 03:18:38.063379+00'),
